    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Open Terminal(iTerm2) in Current Folder]]></title>
    <link href="http://tclh123.github.com/blog/2013/06/14/open-terminal-iterm2-in-current-folder/"/>
    <updated>2013-06-14T15:58:00+08:00</updated>
